## Requirements

### System
- Windows 10/11
- Python 3.11+
- [Ollama](https://ollama.com) installed
- [Android Platform Tools](https://developer.android.com/tools/releases/platform-tools) (for ADB phone app launching)

### Python packages
```bash
pip install speechrecognition pyaudio pygame edge-tts pvporcupine psutil pyautogui requests flask flask-cors
```

